Ikiza cy'indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Bwongereza no mu Bwongereza, tariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) igaragaza imiterere nk'iyo mu bihugu by'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byemeza ko nubwo mu rwego rutandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere byihuse mu bihugu byose.
Bishingiye ku bumenyi buturuka mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibitaro bifite ubuvuzi bwimbitse, byagombye kongera ubushobozi bwo kwitegura umubare w'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bazakenera ubuvuzi, by'umwihariko kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, itsinda ry'abarwayi ba pneumonia batazwi ryatangajwe mu ntara ya Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no kwirinda indwara cyatangaje ko icyo cyorezo ari coronavirus nshya yiswe coronavirus ikomeye yo guhumeka coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, uburwayi bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwiswe coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubuhamya bugaragaza ko hafi 80<0x25> by'abantu bafite COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ko barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa na pneumonia cyangwa idafite, kandi abenshi muri bo bagakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14<0x25>, COVID-19 igenda iba indwara ikomeye cyane isaba kujyanwa mu bitaro mu gihe abasigaye 6<0x25> bafite indwara zikomeye zisaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abahitanywe n'indwara ya Covid-19 ungana na 4<0x25>.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, dusuzuma imiterere ya COVID-19 muri buri karere k'ubukungu bw'u Burayi/Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) maze tuyigereranye n'intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Tugereranyije kandi umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani muri 31 Mutarama<0xE2><0x80><0x93>15 Werurwe 2020.
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EAC n'u Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira ndetse n'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi muri iki gihe rikurikira iki gihugu.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari cyorezo.
Mu ngingo ya 5 Werurwe 2020 ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al yavuze ku bantu ba mbere b'i Burayi bemeje ko barwaye COVID-19 nk'uko byatangajwe n'Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye.
Muri EU/EEA, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'u Bufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020, mu bantu bavuye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yagaragaye mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EA na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (UK), aho hagati ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hakubiyemo abarwayi 39,768 n'abagera kuri 1,727 bahitanywe n'indwara 17,750 n'abagera ku 1.441 baturutse mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kumenya umubare w'abarwayi ba Covid-19 n'ibibazo by'ingutu
Mu kigo cy'ubumwe bw'u Burayi gishinzwe kurinda no kugenzura indwara (ECDC), umubare w'abarwayi ba Covid-19 mu gihugu hose, uboneka gusa ku isoko ryemewe n'amategeko nka Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, abayobozi b'igihugu n'akarere ndetse na OMS, bavugururwa buri munsi saa kumi n'imwe z'umugoroba.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma imiterere ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kuyagereranya n'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'ikimenyetso cy'ikwirakwizwa ry'abarwayi ba Covid-19, twabaranye iminsi 14 igabanuka ry'abarwayi ba COVID-19, bityo tugasuzuma uburyo busanzwe bwa COVID-19, buri gihugu cya EU/EA n'Ubwongereza, mu gihe cya 1 Mutarama<0xE2><0x80><0x93>15 Werurwe 2020.
Twatanze kandi umubare wiyongereye w'abarwayi bamenyekanye muri buri gihugu kuva tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cya 31 Mutarama<0xE2><0x80><0x93>15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EAC no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'iminsi 14 y'indwara za COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange yakurikiye iyo ya Hubei Province (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Kuri EU/EA n'Ubwongereza muri rusange, ingaruka za COVID-19 zatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma byiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho byiyongereye).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abarwayi bavugwaga baturutse mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose byo muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje imyifatire nk'iyo y'igabanuka ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 (ibikoresho byiyongereye).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare wiyongereye w'abarwayi ba COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cya 31 Mutarama<0xE2><0x80><0x93>15 Werurwe 2020.
Yakomeje avuga ko mu masaha ya saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba, ibihugu 15 byo muri EU/EAE n'Ubwongereza byamaze gutangaza umubare w'abanduye ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa mbere cyangwa hasi.
Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ugenda wiyongera byihuse muri EU/EA na UK.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko icyorezo cya Covid-19 kigenda gitera imbere ku muvuduko ungana mu bihugu byose.
Ibi birashoboka nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihugu, ndetse n'ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'indwara mu bihugu n'indi protocol itandukanye mu guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo basuzumwe COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'u Butaliyani bavuze ko mu bice 10<0x25> by'abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bwimbitse n'itangazamakuru, bavuze ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi muri ibyo bice byamaze kugera ku rugero runini.
Imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro no/cyangwa ikigo cy'ubuvuzi bukabije ubu iboneka ku rugero rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6<0x25> gusa na 1<0x25>, mu buryo bunyuranye (amakuru atagaragajwe).
Icyakora, bagomba gukusanywa mu buryo bwikora kugira ngo barusheho gukurikirana amakuru ajyanye n'umubare w'abarwayi bavugwa ndetse n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwerekanye itandukaniro rinini mu kuboneka kw'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwimbitse n'ubuvuzi mu Burayi, kuva kuri 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 ku baturage 100,000 bo muri Portugal.
Ibi bisobanuye ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo urenze uw'u Butaliyani (112.5, ubuvuzi bwimbitse n'ubuvuzi bwihariye ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Imibare ijyanye no kugabanya ubushobozi bwo kwivuza, hamwe n'ibipimo bya buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza by'ikwirakwizwa ry'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bifitanye isano na <0x26>gt; 90<0x25> bafite ibyago byo kurenga ubushobozi bwo kuryama bwihuse, bahabwa mu ivugurura rya gatandatu rya ECDC ryo gupima ibyago byihuse kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko uburwayi bumaze kugera mu turere tumwe na tumwe two muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi byita ku baturage bizwi, amakuru ku birebana n'uburwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi binini bigomba gushyirwa ahagaragara mu rwego rw'imibare ya 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'u Butaliyani ndetse n'ibindi bihugu birimo bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere byihuse muri EU/EA na UK.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwimbitse byagombye kwitegura uburyo bwo kwandura SARS-CoV-2 mu muryango no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bwimbitse, nko mu turere twanduye mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibiza bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bukora kandi burambuye ni ingenzi mu guteza imbere ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, hamwe n'impinduka kuva ku bufatanye n'uburyo bwo kugabanya, nk'uko umubare w'abarwayi uteganyijwe ushobora kudatanga abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhuza igisubizo cyabo.
Ubushakashatsi bwihuse kandi bwagaragaje ingamba z'ubuzima bwa rubanda zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari amahirwe magufi, aho ibihugu bifite amahirwe yo kongera imihati yabyo yo kugenzura kugira ngo bigabanyirize ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya umuvuduko w'ubuvuzi.
Kutabigeraho, birashoboka ko gahunda z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu byo muri EU/EEA zizahura n'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bwimbitse mu minsi iri imbere cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Ikiza cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu cyahitanye abantu barenga 3,000 kandi cyanduza abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no ahandi ku isi.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV, yatumye SARS igera ku bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na yo ishobora kwandura n’indwara z’udukoko kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk’ibyo binyuze mu buryo busa n’ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite uburemere buke n'impfu nyinshi kurusha SARS, ariko igira ingaruka nyinshi ku bageze mu za bukuru kurusha abakiri bato n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongereye w'ibitabo bijyanye n'icyorezo, iki gice kigerageza gutanga isesengura ryimbitse kandi ryimbitse ryerekeye ubushakashatsi bwihuse.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze bijyanye na Epidemiology, Etiology, Virology, Gusuzuma, Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Ubuhanuzi, n'Uburinzi bw'Iki cyorezo.
Nubwo ibibazo byinshi bisaba ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi nyandiko ifasha mu gusobanukirwa no gukuraho iyi ndwara.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi tariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana kandi rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabiwe kuguma mu nzu mu biruhuko byose no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo gishya.
Iyi virusi ifatanye cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateye indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (SARS) mu 2003; ku bw'ibyo, yahawe izina SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi icyo cyorezo cyiswe CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyahise gikwirakwira hirya no hino mu gihugu ndetse no mu bindi bice 50 ku isi hose.
Ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi yatumye abantu barenga 80,000 banduye Covid-19, mu gihe abarwayi barenga 40,000 bavuyemo ndetse n'abarenga 3000 bahitanywe n'icyo cyorezo.
OMS ivuga ko COVID-19 ari "umubare w'umwanzi wo mu ruhame" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, impapuro zirenga 200 zasohotse kuri COVID-19 zirimo virus, indwara, etiology, ubushakashatsi, n'ubuvuzi kuva raporo ya mbere ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje gukurikirana kwa virusi itandukanye n'abarwayi benshi.
Iri tangazo rigamije kugaragaza impinduka mu bushakashatsi bushya kandi bwihuse mu karere ka Rubavu.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tuzagerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'izindi ndwara zitera CoV, syndrome y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyabaye mu 2012).
Tugiye kandi gusuzuma ibyo twize ku birebana n'indwara n'uburwayi ndetse n'ibibazo byihutirwa.
CoVs zikunze gufatwa nk'indwara zitera indwara ziterwa n'abantu, cyane cyane zitera 15<0x25> by'imbeho zikunze kugaragara.
Ariko kandi, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na CoVs nyinshi cyane, ni ukuvuga SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zateye ikwirakwira rya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabie Saoudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze zarakwirakwijwe mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite indwara ziteye ubwoba n'urupfu.
Covid-19 nicyo gitero cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara muri Fig.Fig.1,1, abarwaye umusonga batazwi batangajwe bwa mbere kuva mu mujyi wa Wuhan tariki 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza muri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, umukino wa CoV wafunguwe.
Tariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020 nibwo hamenyekanye umurwayi wa mbere wishwe na Wuhan.
Iki cyorezo cyahise gikwirakwira hirya no hino mu mijyi, mu turere no mu bihugu bituranye.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, byatangajwe ko indwara y'abaganga yanduye, igaragaza ko umuntu ashobora kwandura.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe n'imodoka zose za Leta zahagaritswe.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara, bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 barwaye indwara yemejwe, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye neza n'isoko ry'ibiribwa ry'inyanja rya Wuhan ryafatwaga nk'aho ari ahantu ho gutangira kwandura iyi ndwara iva ku nyamaswa itazwi.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo ari ikibazo gikomeye ku isi.
Muri iyi raporo, iyi ndwara yamaze gukwirakwira hirya no hino mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi (Fig.2).
Uko ibintu bigenda bigenda bihindagurika, haracyari icyemezo cy'uko iki cyorezo kigenda gihitana abantu benshi ndetse n'uburemere bw'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 barimo abarwayi 4,021 bemeje Covid-19 bwagaragaje ibimenyetso bishya by'icyorezo nk'ibi bikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX<0x5F>rHPXA1qqhhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduye abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane bafite imyaka 30-65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7<0x25>) cy'abarwaye iyi ndwara bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa ni bo bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduye abagabo benshi (0.31/100,000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100,000).
