Umubare w'abamaze guhitanwa n'urupfu wabaye mu gihe cy'iminsi 9.5 (4.8-13).
Umubare w'ibanze w'ibyana (R0) wari 3.77 (95<0x25> CI: 3.51-4.05), kandi R0 yavuguruwe yari 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abarwaye iyi ndwara wiyongereye cyane mbere ya tariki ya 23 Mutarama 2020, ugereranyije n'igihe cy'imodoka nyinshi mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Impfu z'abarwayi bafite indwara zemejwe ni 1.44<0x25> (95<0x25> CI: 1.1-1.86<0x25>), kandi impungenge z'abarwayi bose ni 3.06<0x25> (95<0x25> CI: 2.02-4.59<0x25>).
