Kugeza ubu, kubera kutagira umuti ukomeye kandi wihariye wa COVID-19, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti ikomeye ku barwayi bafite urumuri rw'ibimenyetso bigereranyije cyangwa ku bakize bavuye mu byiciro bikomeye.
