Urugero, mu bihugu byinshi byo muri Afurika byo mu cyaro, gukaraba intoki za tapi hafi ya buri nzu yigenga cyangwa ya rubanda ntibyoroshye, nubwo hari uburyo bworoshye bwo gukaraba intoki.
Ariko kandi, imibare yo gukaraba intoki yoroshye ishobora no kuba iterwa n'imyitwarire mibi aho kuba idafite isupu cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere no gushyigikira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki, kongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho, ni ngombwa gusuzuma no kugenzura.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ubushakashatsi bwa 70 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku muryango bufasha mu kongera gukaraba intoki muri LMIC, mu gihe imyitozo yo gucuruza mu muryango idakora neza.Urugero rumwe rwo gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Three Star Approach" ya UNICEF itera inkunga amashuri gufata intambwe zoroshye kandi zita agaciro kugira ngo abanyeshuri bajye basukura mu ntoyi, hagati mu zindi.
Iyo amashuri ageze ku rwego rwo hasi, ashobora kuva ku rwego rumwe agera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki bikorerwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urugero rw'impinduka zigamije guteza imbere imyitwarire.Ibi byatewe n'icyorezo cya coronavirus cya 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije ko hashyirwaho emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere bifite akamaro kanini ku bijyanye n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bugaragaza ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifite akamaro kanini ugereranyije n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku n'isuku.
Umumaro wo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu - cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu bihe bigoye nka ba nyina bari baherutse kuvuka cyangwa bakomeretse mu bitaro - wamenyekanye bwa mbere hagati mu kinyejana cya 19 n'ikinyejana cya 19 n'abapayiniya babiri b'isuku y'amaboko: umuganga wo muri Hungary Ignaz Semmelweis wakoze i Vienna, Austria na Florence Nightingale, umushingizi w'icyongereza.
Muri icyo gihe, abantu benshi bemeraga ko indwara zandurira mu misemburo mibi yitwa miasmas.
Mu myaka ya 1980, indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa ndetse n'indwara zifashishwa n'ubuvuzi, byatumye ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kigenzura no kurwanya indwara kirushaho guteza imbere isuku y'amaboko nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Ikiza cy'ingurube cyaduka mu 2009 ndetse n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye ibihugu byinshi birushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune kugira ngo birinde indwara zandura.
Urugero, ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga byo gukaraba intoki byamanitswe hafi y'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu mazu y'abantu no mu mazu y'inyubako z'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege mu Budage.
Ijambo "gukaraba intoki" risobanuye ko umuntu adashaka kugira inshingano zo gukora ikintu cyangwa kugishyira mu bikorwa.
Bikomoka mu murongo wa Bibiliya muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yagejejeho umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko yahindutse ijambo rikoreshwa cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'Icyongereza.
Mu gitabo cyitwa Shakespeare's Macbeth, Lady Macbeth yatangiye gukaraba intoki ze mu buryo bw'agahato mu kugerageza gusukura umurambo w'umuntu utekereza, ahagarariye umutimanama we urangwa n'icyaha yakoze kandi agatuma umugabo we akora icyaha.
Bavuga kandi ko abantu bamaze gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, bakanagira agaciro ko gukaraba intoki.
Ku rundi ruhande, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza gutyo, ntibashobora kwifatanya n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku, nko kwitanga.
Amadini asaba gukaraba intoki ku bw'intego z'isuku n'iz'ikigereranyo.Ibimenyetso byo gukaraba intoki, gukoresha amazi ariko nta sabuni yo gukaraba intoki, ni igice cy'imigenzo yo gukaraba intoki mu madini menshi, harimo ukwemera kw'aba Bahá'í, ubuhindu, tevila na yabitadayim mu idini y'Abayahudi, Lavabo mu bukirisitu, na Wudhu mu idini ya Isilamu.
