Igenzura ry'akazi rya COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukoresha umutekano w'akazi n'uburyo bw'ubuzima mu kugenzura ibyago byo kwirinda Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza ibyago mu kazi biterwa n'umurimo n'akazi, bishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago by'inkomoko z'indwara, uburebure bw'indwara mu baturage, n'impamvu z'impanuka z'abakozi bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima n'Ubuzima muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (OSHA), rivuga ko imirimo yo kuboneza urubyaro igabanya imikorere y'abakozi ba Leta n'abandi bakozi, iyo hafashwe ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara, harimo no gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo niba barwaye, guhumeka, no gukomeza gusukura no kwandura ibidukikije.
Imirimo yo guhangana n'ibiza ikubiyemo isaba ko habaho guhura kenshi cyangwa hafi n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe no kwandura mu muryango cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi bikubiyemo abakozi bahura n'abaturage muri rusange, urugero nko mu mashuri, mu bigo by'akazi byiganjemo abantu benshi, hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bihanitse.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda iki cyorezo, hakubiyemo guhumeka hakoreshejwe filters zo mu kirere zifite ubushobozi buhanitse, abarinzi b'umwijima n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bihari mu gihe umuntu ufite COVID-19 yahuye na byo.
