Aho ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, imiyoborere myiza kurusha izindi ni imiyoborere y'ikoranabuhanga, ikurikiranwa n'imiyoborere y'ubuyobozi, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
