B'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifatanye n'urwego rw'ikirere mu mahaha, imitsi, umutima, impyiko n'inda.
ACE2 irwanya ibikorwa bya enzyme ijyanye na angiotensin-converting (ACE) mu kugabanya umubare wa angiotensin-II no kwiyongera Ang(1-7) bituma igira intego yihariye yo kuvura indwara z'umutima.ACE2 kandi ikora nk'ahantu ho kwinjira mu turemangingo twa coronavirus tumwe.
Akenshi iyo umuntu asobanukiwe iby'iyo ndwara yitwa H.E.2.
Angiotensin-convert enzyme 2 ni zinc ifite ibyuma by'umubiri biri ku butaka bwa endothelial n'ibindi bice.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 igizwe n'igice cya N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal collerin renal amino acid conductor domain.
ACE2 ni poroteyine y'ubwoko bumwe bw'ubwoko bwa membrane, hamwe na domain yayo ikora ya enzymatic igaragara hejuru y'uturemangingo tw'ibihaha n'ibindi bihimba.
Icyiciro cya ACE2 kigizwe n'ikindi kimenyetso cy'ubwoko bwa transmembrance gifatwa n'izindi enzyme zizwi nka poroteyine y'ubutaka, kandi poroteyine zikomoka mu maraso zishyirwa mu maraso maze amaherezo zigashyirwa mu myunyu.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifitanye isano n'urusobe rw'uturemangingo tw'ubuhumekero cyane ubwoko bwa II alveolar cells, enterocytes y'utugingo ngengabuzima duto duto tw'amagufa, ateri y'umubiri n'utugingo ngengabuzima dusa neza mu ngingo nyinshi.
Imvugo ya ACE2 mRNA iboneka kandi muri cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, na brainstem.
Igice cya mbere cy'umushinga wa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'umushinga w'ubufatanye n'ubuyobozi bwa ACE.
ACE ifata umusemburo wa angiotensin I muri vasoconstricting angiotensin II.
ACE2 na yo ifata carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine ikomoka kuri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Phe-Phe) ikongera ikayishyira muri vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-I-P-P-P-P-Hi-Hi-Hi-Hi-Hi-Hi-His).
ACE2 ishobora kandi guhuza izindi peptide nyinshi harimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura ubucukuzi bwubucukuzi bwubucukuzi bwa amino aside itwara SLC6A19 kandi ifite uruhare mu burwayi bwa Hartnup.
Nk'uko poroteyine ya transmembrane, ACE2 ikora nk'igice nyamukuru cyinjira mu turemangingo twa coronavirus zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (Virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (Virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, gufunga poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku kirwa cya Enzymatic domain ya ACE2 ku butaka bw'uturemangingo, bivamo endocytosis no gushyirwamo virusi ndetse na enzyme mu binyabuzima biri mu turemangingo.
